intervention.description:
The intervention includes a total of 15 virtual meetings and aims to achieve a weight loss of 0.8 to 1% of the initial weight per week.
This will include 3 successive phases:
A significant calorie restriction (800 kcal / day) for a period of 4 weeks;
A moderate calorie restriction (minimum deficit of 500 kcal / day) for a period of 4 weeks;
A maintenance phase of weight loss for 16 weeks.
